00:02:04.420 --> 00:02:08.660
You know, electric heaters don't have a vent,
because they don't have any fuel to burn.

00:02:08.660 --> 00:02:12.790
They make them indoor or outdoor model on
these tankless heaters.

00:02:12.790 --> 00:02:15.670
Either way, you're gonna have to have some
of the fundamental things that you're gonna

00:02:15.670 --> 00:02:20.360
need for one of the conventional tank hot
water heaters: You're gonna need a source

00:02:20.360 --> 00:02:22.810
of electricity to ignite the fuel to heat
the water.

00:02:22.810 --> 00:02:25.100
